<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_b78eb63e-4b56-4fc3-a76f-516b5a2109a0" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/></meta><sptc>H2O1</sptc><title id="_9b9538ad-243a-4762-92dd-c84159269dc8">Objective</title><archive-num>2019: O2.2</archive-num><subclause id="_c418304a-e843-4ae2-a453-c3f395cef30b" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_92dcda9c-440e-43b4-a6e9-a21006af35f8">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>The Objective is to—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_eaa93790-a965-457f-8592-cc7b3d08ae16">safeguard occupants from illness or injury and protect the building from damage caused by—<ol><li><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1486_26.7.0.xml#_02c3900f-c9bb-470b-93f4-d71555f2fea7" id="_9ac41019-30a1-4131-8964-bd34cc1edec6" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">surface water</xref>; and</li><li>external water entering a building; and</li><li>the accumulation of internal moisture in a building; and</li><li>discharge of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_36a5bfcc-9821-4caa-9030-d1d4ee66782b" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref> waste water; and</li><li>rising damp; and</li></ol></li><li id="_5b997edd-1d4a-4842-ac30-378594b2312a">protect other property from damage caused by—<ol><li>redirected <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1486_26.7.0.xml#_02c3900f-c9bb-470b-93f4-d71555f2fea7" id="_de3dce32-0a75-4e72-b066-46f940516040" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">surface water</xref>; and</li><li>the discharge of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_ef14cd4a-3683-4170-8605-8a79b1e3592f" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref> waste water.</li></ol></li></ol></subclause></clause>